########################################
Open Stack automatic installation script
########################################

1)In order to start installation just execute 'Juno_install.sh' file as './Juno_install.sh'.
2)This script is only for single node installation.
3)Make sure to enter correct input when script prompts for user input.
4)Edit the /etc/hosts file to contain the following:
	
	# controller
	10.0.0.11 controller
	# compute1
	10.0.0.31 compute1

4)Creation of networks and volume groups are out of scope for this script.
5)User need to adjust physical network and vlan ids based on their requirement in neutron plugin configuration.
6)Attaching physical NIC of server to bridge 'br-ex' is not done in the script. User should attach selected interface to bridge based on their requirement.
